==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Udderless
<hw>Ud"der*less</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Destitute or
deprived of an udder.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Hence, without mother's milk; motherless; <as>as,
<ex>udderless</ex> lambs</as>.</def> <mark>[Poetic]</mark>
<rj><au>Keats.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Udometer</ent>⟦br⟧
